(15, 4, 72, 0, 4, '<p>This unique wall clock will look beautiful in your kitchen, or any room in your home. The bright and beautiful colors really stand out which makes this clock so beautiful and unique. There are shiny gold and hot pink flower designs covering beautiful shades of teal and other shades of blue. The gold, blue and pink colors are sure to brighten your day. </p><p>And remember that at Shannybeebo, I specialize in creating works of functional art to enhance your space. If you donÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã‚Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¬&trade;t see a clock that fulfills your design needs, send me a convo and I will work with you to create your own clock according to your design specifications.</p> '),
